POSTGRES_1_MERGE_DEF POSTGRES_1::public.business-licences EXACT public.business-licences DEFLINE postgres_type,postgres_none,postgres_sql_where_clause,folderyear<lt>space<gt>=<lt>space<gt><lt>apos<gt>26<lt>apos<gt>,postgres_sql_statement,,folderyear,varchar,licencersn,varchar,licencenumber,varchar,licencerevisionnumber,varchar,businessname,varchar,businesstradename,varchar,status,varchar,issueddate,timestamp,expireddate,date,businesstype,varchar,businesssubtype,varchar,unit,varchar,unittype,varchar,house,varchar,street,varchar,city,varchar,province,varchar,country,varchar,postalcode,varchar,localarea,varchar,numberofemployees,float8,feepaid,float8,extractdate,timestamp
